<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mesh_networking&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.pdos.lcs.mit.edu/roofnet/" class="external text" title="http://www.pdos.lcs.mit.edu/roofnet/" rel="nofollow">MIT Roofnet</a> A research project at MIT that forms the basis of roofnet / <a href="/wiki/Meraki" title="Meraki">Meraki</a> mesh networks</li>
<li><a href="http://www.wing-project.org" class="external text" title="http://www.wing-project.org" rel="nofollow">WING Project</a> Wireless Mesh Network distribution based on the roofnet source code</li>
<li><a href="http://www.meshdynamics.com/documents/Mesh_Mining_July08.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.meshdynamics.com/documents/Mesh_Mining_July08.pdf" rel="nofollow">Miners Give a Nod to Nodes</a> Reprint from Mission Critical Magazine on successful deployment of mesh in mines</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mit.edu/~medard/itmanet" class="external text" title="http://www.mit.edu/~medard/itmanet" rel="nofollow">DARPA's ITMANET program and the FLoWS Project</a> Investigating Fundamental Performance Limits of MANETS</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ted.com/talks/view/id/212" class="external text" title="http://www.ted.com/talks/view/id/212" rel="nofollow">Robin Chase discusses Zipcar and Mesh networking</a> Robin Chase talks at the Ted conference about the future of mesh networking and eco-technology</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mesh-networks.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.mesh-networks.org/" rel="nofollow">Mesh Networks Research Group</a> Projects and tutorials' compilation related to the Wireless Mesh Networks</li>
</ul>


